      <h2>Step 3 - Observe Student</h3>
      <p>After creating a session record, you are ready to start observing.</p>
      <h3>Submitting an Observation</h3>
      <p>Please note that <span class="highlight-red">all observations are automatically submitted at the end of each interval</span>.  Therefore, no action is required to store the results of an interval.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-5">
      <h3>Start Timer</h3>
      <p>When you are ready to begin observing, click the "Start Timer" button. When clicked, the timer will start counting down by the interval you included in the sessions create form.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-offset-0 col-sm-5">
